COMMANDS
--------

UV spectra in gas phase with MOLCAS

O.- Preparation of the "multispec" simulation
a) Run "multispec" to prepare the scripts and folders

1.- Preparation of the molecular geom in gaussian (in gaussian folder)
a) Geom opt and Freq with DFT with Gaussian
b) ./gaus2optxyz.sh --->  to extract the optimized xyz geom from opt+freq gaussian log 

2.- NEA sampling (in newtonX folder)
a) ./gaus2nx.sh --->  to generate the sampling in final_output file 
                      using the opt+freq gaussian log 
b) ./convert_nx_xyz.sh ---> to create all the xyz coordinates files of the NEA
c) molden {file snaps} ---> to visualize the geoms

3.- (Optional) Starting orbitals (in molcas.orb folder)

4.- Molcas computations of VEE and f (in molcas.vee folder)
a) Edit molcas_input.template files # Input keywords for Molcas
b) ./generate_inps_molcas.sh  
c) Edit template_lzMolcas with yous job_submit script
d)

3.- cross section programs

